awards.description:
As part of the Solutions4HealthFutures team, I developed a strategy to disseminate the contents of the report of the Lancet-Financial Times Commission Governing Health Futures 2030: growing up in a digital world. The strategy comprises:
- A multi-stage advocacy campaign with regional report launches that culminate in a Global Summit;
- The creation of digital assets, such as interactive visual adaptations of key report findings and recommendations;
- Knowledge collection, mapping, and archiving through the development of an online platform;
- Workshops leading up to regional launches that focus on providing youth a voice in discussions around the development of digital health governance by letting them actively engage with policymakers and change agents;
- A post-regional launch workshop with policymakers and change agents to materialise the insights of the pre-launch workshop and the regional launch
